        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Winter Gritting &amp; Severe Weather</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">How LCC keeps Burnley&rsquo;s roads moving in winter</p>
        </div>

        <div class="winter-content">
          <div class="winter-info">
            <p>
              Lancashire County Council grits priority routes (P1) when temperatures are forecast to drop
              below zero. P1 routes include all A and B roads, bus routes, and roads to hospitals and fire stations.
              Secondary routes (P2) are treated during prolonged severe weather.
            </p>
            <p>
              Burnley sits at the foot of the Pennines with several high-altitude routes (Cliviger Gorge,
              Deerplay Moor, Worsthorne) that are particularly vulnerable to ice and snow. The A646 through
              the Cliviger Gorge toward Todmorden is one of the most weather-affected routes in East Lancashire.
            </p>
            <div class="winter-links">
              <a href="https://www.lancashire.gov.uk/roads-parking-and-travel/roads/gritting/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                LCC Gritting Routes &amp; Schedule
                <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.lancashire.gov.uk/roads-parking-and-travel/roads/gritting/grit-bins/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                Request a Grit Bin
                <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"></path><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"></line></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="winter-routes">
            <h3>Key Routes at Risk</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>A646 Cliviger Gorge</strong> &mdash; High altitude, exposed, frequent closures</li>
              <li><strong>A671 Deerplay Moor</strong> &mdash; Elevated moorland crossing to Bacup</li>
              <li><strong>Worsthorne / Hurstwood</strong> &mdash; Elevated villages, narrow roads</li>
              <li><strong>M65 J10-14</strong> &mdash; LCC-maintained section, exposed at higher elevation</li>
              <li><strong>Haggate / Briercliffe Road</strong> &mdash; Higher ground, steep gradients</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>
